    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Female holotype of Spinoliella confusa Gonzalez and Engel, new species. A. Facial view. B. Detail of mesoscutum, mesoscutellum, and metanotum in dorsal view. C. Metabasitibial plate. D. Dorsal habitus. E. Lateral habitus. F. Pygidial plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5407158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5407160>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male paratype of Spinoliella confusa Gonzalez and Engel, new species from Elqui Province, Pangue, Chile (PCYU). A. Facial view. B. Lateral habitus. C. Dorsal habitus. D. Detail of mesoscutum, mesoscutellum, and metanotum in dorsal view. E. Metabasitibial plate. F. Metasomal S7. G. Metasomal S8. H. Genital capsule in dorsal (left half) and ventral (right half) views. I. Lateral aspect of genital capsule." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5407160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

